<a href="#agile-update" name="agile-update"></a><table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="full-block" style="border-collapse:collapse; " ><tr ><td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" ><table cellpadding="40" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; " ><tr ><td align="left" valign="middle" class="text-block" style="padding-bottom:10px; color:#666666; font-size:13px; line-height:22px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="agile-update-title" style="padding-bottom:20px; " ><img src="http://play.gopivotal.com/rs/pivotal/images/nl-portrait-jfraser.png" alt="Janice Fraser" align="right" style="display: block;"> <span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px; line-height: 16px;">AGILE UPDATE</span><br>
<span style="margin:0; font-size:20px; font-weight:bold; line-height:24px; text-transform:uppercase;">Agile, Lean, and a Transformation Blueprint</span><br>
<span style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;"><a href="https://gopivotal-com.socialcast.com/users/1080303-janicefraser" style="color:#3ea7bc; text-decoration:none;">Janice Fraser</a>, Director, Innovation Practice, Pivotal</span></div>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; " ><tr ><td align="left" valign="top" class="stack" style="color:#666666; font-size:14px; line-height:22px; padding-bottom:20px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="agile-update-entry" ><p>Last month, we announced a fantastic partnership between <a target="_blank" style="color:#3ea7bc; text-decoration:none;" href="http://blog.pivotal.io/pivotal/news-2/pivotal-and-eric-ries-partners-for-enterprise-transformation">Pivotal and Eric Ries,</a> the best-selling author of <a target="_blank" style="color:#3ea7bc; text-decoration:none;" href="http://theleanstartup.com/">The Lean Startup</a>. Eric has been a long-time friend of Pivotal Labs, and has asked Pivotal to be a key partner in the launch of his latest, limited-edition book project, <a target="_blank" style="color:#3ea7bc; text-decoration:none;" href="https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/881308232/only-on-kickstarter-the-leaders-guide-by-eric-ries">The Leader's Guide</a>. In the book, Eric will share the tools, techniques and lessons that he uses with Fortune 1000 companies like GE and Intuit.<br>
<br>
But there is much more to come…<br>
<br>
Eric understands how challenging agile transformation can be. "I’ve seen a lot of people who immediately “got” it," he says. But they "struggle after experiencing the challenges that come when trying to build a new company, or transform an existing one."<br>
<br>
We're thrilled to announce that Pivotal Labs' <a target="_blank" style="color:#3ea7bc; text-decoration:none;" href="https://docs.google.com/a/pivotal.io/viewer?a=v&amp;pid=sites&amp;srcid=cGl2b3RhbC5pb3xwaXZvdGFsd2lraXxneDo0NjdhMWNlMzBlNTUyMzcw">Innovation Practice</a> will be among the first in the world to put the Leader's Guide into practice. Our Innovation Practice provides workshops that help clients make bold steps and navigate difficult decisions on the path to becoming successful digital companies.<br>
<br>
Over the coming months, and with the help of Eric Ries, Pivotal will be developing a one-day workshop to introduce the concepts, tools and techniques outlined in the Lean Startup and Leader's Guide – offering a blueprint for transformation.<br>
<br>
Pivotal Labs facilitators will deliver Innovation Workshops in 11 cities, starting in October.<br>
<br>
Stay tuned for details!</p>
</div>
